abstract: Princess Mary of Denmark is making a series of appearance in New York City with her husband Prince Frederik, the heir to the Danish throne.
snippet: Princess Mary of Denmark, the wife of the crown prince, stopped by a settlement house in Long Island City that has a Danish connection.
